&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.python.org/3.13/library/functions.html&#34;&gt;Built-in Functions — Python 3.13.2 documentation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.python.org/3.13/library/bisect.html&#34;&gt;bisect — Array bisection algorithm — Python 3.13.2 documentation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.python.org/3/library/itertools.html&#34;&gt;itertools — Functions creating iterators for efficient looping — Python 3.13.2 documentation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
